_sText:
I made this map because me and some of my friends enjoyed playing He_glass in 1.6.

First release.

HDR lit, but there are no cubemaps, so your knifes and HE nades will be a little wierd.

Nades are a little hard to see, but after a while you will know where they are.

Credits to who ever made He_glass in 1.6.
